title: Added additional notification settings and notification filtering.
message:
Added additional notification settings and notification filtering.
Notifications are now only applied to WSPRs with a time stamp in the update interval.

title: Added multiple main screen layouts.  The main screen can now display gridsquare,…
message:
Added multiple main screen layouts.  The main screen can now display gridsquare, callsign, or gridsquare+callsign.  Made grid/call column slightly wider.
Avoid azimuth NaN calculation.
Incremented version number.

title: Created tag wspr-v5, removed write-to-SD permission.
message: Created tag wspr-v5, removed write-to-SD permission.

title: Added 'frequency' to database UNIQUE criteria to further avoid near-duplicate…
message:
Added 'frequency' to database UNIQUE criteria to further avoid near-duplicate items not being stored.
Added an overall filter enable, and the capability to filter as an OR, in addition to AND.
Incremented version.

title: Added src folder back in.
